        <item>
            <title>iOS 19 更多设计细节曝光，WWDC 2025 将发布近年最大更新</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/heres-another-look-at-the-glassy-ios-19-design-but-apple-has-bigger-plans/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 11:35:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299487</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 已正式公布 WWDC 2025 将于 6 月 9 日至 13 日举行，届时将发布 iOS 19 等全新软件平台。据传，iOS 19 将迎来 Apple 历史上最具规模的软件更新。爆料者 Jon Prosser 近日分享了 iOS 19 的设计细节，展示其「玻璃风」视觉效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>Jon Prosser 最新影片透露了 iOS 19 的设计特色，采用「玻璃风、visionOS 主题」风格，涵盖应用程式、按钮及键盘等元素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>新设计强调圆润美学与光泽感，界面边缘仿佛从荧幕中「浮现」。键盘尤为突出，几乎呈现悬浮效果，与 Apple Sports 及 Apple Invites 应用程式中的设计细节有相似之处。此外锁定荧幕界面维持功能不变，但通知及按钮增添半透明与 3D 浮动效果，设定选项及弹出式视窗亦采用更柔和的圆角设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-7.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>Jon Prosser 早前曾展示过 iOS 19 的相机及讯息应用程式模型，包含气泡状导航按钮及更圆润的界面元素。其补充指，目前曝光的版本未见主荧幕采用圆形应用图标，但不排除未来调整可能。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6-694x347.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="347" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6-694x347.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/introducingios19_exc-6.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><p>而彭博社记者 Mark Gurman 则透露目前流传的 iOS 19 图像并非最终版本， Apple 还有更多计划未曝光，6 月将有更多惊喜。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">iOS 19 images floating around aren&#8217;t representative of what we&#8217;ll see at WWDC. They look to be based on either very old builds or vague descriptions, missing key features. Expect more from Apple in June. Regardless, mockups &#8211; real or not &#8211; are always exciting for Apple watchers.</p><p>— Mark Gurman (@markgurman) <a href="https://twitter.com/markgurman/status/1904676788669690087?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">March 25, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>iOS 19 预计于 WWDC 2025 亮相后，随即推出开发者测试版，公测版则于数周后发布，最终版本或于 2025 年 9 月或 10 月与新 iPhone 一同登场。业界预测，除视觉革新外，Apple 可能整合 Apple Intelligence 功能，如更智能的 Siri 或端到端加密 RCS 讯息。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_72054"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2RKrbTkP53M?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://9to5mac.com/2025/03/25/ios-19-update-new-design-more-plans/">9to5mac</a>、<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2RKrbTkP53M">fpt.@YouTube</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
