        <item>
            <title>电动三轮车队会展入闸惹争议，港铁：行动辅助装置符合尺寸要求</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/electric-wheel-chair-in-mtr/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=electric-wheel-chair-in-mtr</link>
