            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日港铁会展站出现一队由 4 部三轮电动代步车组成的「车队」，在职员协助下通过闸机出站，相关片段在网络迅速流传，引发热议。港铁回应指，涉事乘客为行动不便人士，所用设备符合港铁尺寸要求。该些电动代步车被视为医疗用途的行动辅助工具，毋须根据《道路交通条例》领牌即可使用。消委会早于 2025 年 1 月建议，电动轮椅应符合国际安全标准并限速（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/16/consumer-concil-said-electric-wheelchair-rent-can-be-six-times/life-tech/health/">相关报道</a>），惟至今未见具体法例跟进。</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="threadsdownloader.com_77946e" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1069500801?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲影片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>片段显示，4 名人士驾驶款式相似的三轮电动代步车，在港铁职员协助下有序通过阔闸机，其中一车旁挂有拐杖，有网友指或显示使用者有行动困难。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39-516x580.jpg" alt="" width="516" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39-516x580.jpg 516w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250326_4_54_39.jpg 630w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 516px" /><br /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644921.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299515" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644907.jpg 678w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>有网民引用港铁守则列明，轮椅及电动轮椅仅限行动不便人士使用，总重不得超 200 公斤，尺寸限制为 1200 毫米（长）× 700 毫米（阔），行驶速度应与步行相若（不高于时速 6 公里）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139-435x580.jpg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139-435x580.jpg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/485904571_1787723139.jpg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>港铁强调，职员当时协助有需要人士，同时维持车站秩序。据港铁网站资料，持有残疾人士登记证或医生证明的人士，可使用符合规定的行动辅助设备。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299512" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938-434x580.jpg" alt="" width="434" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938-434x580.jpg 434w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644938.jpg 673w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 434px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299513" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930-437x580.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930-437x580.jpg 437w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032644930.jpg 678w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 437px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n xd10rxx x1sy0etr x17r0tee x972fbf xcfux6l x1qhh985 xm0m39n x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xp07o12 xzmqwrg x1citr7e x1kdxza xt0b8zv" tabindex="0" role="link" href="https://www.threads.net/@tuenmunlocals"><span class="x1lliihq x1plvlek xryxfnj x1n2onr6 x1ji0vk5 x18bv5gf x12jkypp x193iq5w xeuugli x1fj9vlw x13faqbe x1vvkbs x1s928wv xhkezso x1gmr53x x1cpjm7i x1fgarty x1943h6x x1i0vuye xjohtrz x1s688f xp07o12 x1yc453h x2lah0s" dir="auto" translate="no"><span class="x1lliihq x193iq5w x6ikm8r x10wlt62 xlyipyv xuxw1ft">tuenmunlocals</span></span></a></p><p>事件反映公众对电动代步车使用的关注，随着人口老化，行动辅助设备需求料增，政府或需加快制定清晰规管框架，平衡便利与安全。港铁或会因应事件更新指引，减少误解。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060310/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%8F%BE-%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A-%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-Juicy%E5%8F%AE?fbclid=IwY2xjawJQmeFleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHU3q2PCeVCkgznbaUVdfXxhJNk5-pjKZHEKeGR_mo2-5rsUnqzApSxdCKQ_aem_TxjEqFwRrS4rNmhhScUmSQ#goog_rewarded">星岛</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060310/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%8F%BE-%E4%B8%89%E8%BC%AA%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9A%8A-%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5-%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%BC%94%E5%8A%A9%E8%A8%AD%E5%82%99%E7%AC%A6%E5%B0%BA%E5%AF%B8%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-Juicy%E5%8F%AE?fbclid=IwY2xjawJQmeFleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHU3q2PCeVCkgznbaUVdfXxhJNk5-pjKZHEKeGR_mo2-5rsUnqzApSxdCKQ_aem_TxjEqFwRrS4rNmhhScUmSQ#goog_rewarded">Yahoo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
