            <title>【教学】GPT 4o 文字 AI 绘图大升级，图中加字更准确 + 斋打字制作漫画都得</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/gpt-4o-ai-graphic2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gpt-4o-ai-graphic2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/26/gpt-4o-ai-graphic2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 10:40:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4o]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1299571</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在这个视觉当道年代，无论是社交媒体、简报设计、还是创意创作，大家总会遇上一个烦恼：「我想画图，但我又不懂画画。」即使你脑海已有画面，画笔一到手却不知从何下笔。这时候，ChatGPT 最新版本 —— GPT-4o 的图片生成功能，便是一个帮到你实现「用嘴画图」的神队友。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299540 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032621139.jpg 1273w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299541 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1-542x580.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1-542x580.jpg 542w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-1.jpg 840w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 542px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299543 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709-609x580.jpg" alt="" width="609" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709-609x580.jpg 609w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032650709.jpg 946w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 609px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1299546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/486576439_1076328911-1.jpg 960w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>这个功能让任何人，只要用文字描述一下，就能立即生成图片，甚至能自订文字、角色表情、场景氛围，连漫画都画得到！以下就以用户实际操作画面与生成图像作例子，带大家一步步了解 GPT-4o 图像生成功能的威力与使用方法。</p><p>ChatGPT 网址：<a href="https://www.chatgpt.com">https://www.chatgpt.com</a></p><p>Sora 网址：<a href="https://sora.com/">https://sora.com</a></p><p>*留意 ChatGPT, Sora 在香港需要透过 VPN 才可使用</p><h2>一、用文字画图？<b>GPT-4o </b>教你什么叫「嘴画力」</h2><p>GPT-4o 图像生成功能的最大突破，是让用户透过自然语言输入描述即可生成图片。从第一张图片可见，用户只需输入「请绘画一张周润发在街边吃烧肉饭的图片」，GPT 便成功生成一张笑容满面的发哥，坐在露天街头，手持叉烧饭开怀进食的画面，背景还有唐楼与招牌，生活感十足。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1299527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="833" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/3abaf2ca1a4b4ae9a80f.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1299528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="555" height="833" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/33dc2be17c7147c3a28d.jpg 600w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 555px" /></a></p><p>这种「精准图像 + 角色情绪 + 明确动作」的输出，可让 GPT-4o 生成质素更高的相片。</p><p>使用方法：</p><ol><li>开启 ChatGPT，选择 GPT-4o 模式。点击三点选项按钮，选择「建立图像」；</li><li>在对话框直接输入想像画面，例如：「请绘画一张周润发很开心在街边吃烧肉饭的图片」。</li><li>若有指定角色表情、背景、物品，可直接列明，愈详细愈精准。</li><li>约 30 秒内即会生成图像。</li></ol><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299526 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-542x580.jpg" alt="" width="542" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247-542x580.jpg 542w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032623247.jpg 840w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 542px" /></a></p><h2>二、可以加字的图片！做梗图、告白图、创意海报无难度</h2><p>今次 GPT 4o AI 绘图的更新，还令图片内可更精准输出中文字或英文字。虽然并非每一次都百分百准确，但你可多给它几次机会，它也可制作出不错的作品。</p><p>例如图片中示范举著写有「我 ❤️ 黎明」纸牌站在红磡体育馆前，GPT-4o 除了能准确生成背景（红馆正门），还能将指定中文字体与纸牌内容准确呈现，整张图极具真实感，仿如新闻照片。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1299530 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508-694x494.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="494" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508-694x494.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025032635508.jpg 1263w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><br /><b>
